    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape your party and venture into the Spiritual Realms where yokai, demons, and divine beings reside. Customize your units to your play style in order to survive the brutal skirmishes and battles you will face.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/0105aef7425ac146e103c19bda3065aa.poster.avif?t=1759935686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/0105aef7425ac146e103c19bda3065aa.webm?t=1759935686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/0105aef7425ac146e103c19bda3065aa.mp4?t=1759935686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 6 unique RPG base classes inspired by Japanese mythology, each with their own promotion paths and special abilities. Further develop their roles within each battle by crafting or looting game-changing gear, and upgrading their talents as they grow stronger.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/7e208017fd2101aa5b785e8978882c1e.avif?t=1759935686\" width=600 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/988ab5d4b9d9995abfc6ce57d93c823f.poster.avif?t=1759935686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/988ab5d4b9d9995abfc6ce57d93c823f.webm?t=1759935686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/988ab5d4b9d9995abfc6ce57d93c823f.mp4?t=1759935686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat in Secrets of Shadows rewards creativity and experimentation. Turn the tides of battle with clever usage of terrain. Manipulate the battlefield conditions to your advantage, or exploit the quirks of your enemies.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/76362bfc999ab577eea9c9a4065c8a59.avif?t=1759935686\" width=600 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from the action and by crafting items for your party, customize and fine tune your loadout. Strike up conversations or trade with vendors and take on optional quests to unlock powerful upgrades before you set on your next adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111150/extras/3d0ebe191f14064b3151e5b3c0c58664.avif?t=1759935686\" width=600 height=216 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deep customization and modernized class-based RPG elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fully hand-designed levels and encounters, with procedurally-generated elements added on replayable levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bonus difficult and varied optional encounters for players that welcome the hardest challenges </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2D hand-placed pixel art and atmospheric soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
